## Step by Step
1. Add a Dataset from url : https://www.kaggle.com/hihunjin/efficientnetpyttorch3d
2. Add a directory path
```python
import sys
sys.path.append('../input/efficientnetpyttorch3d/EfficientNet-PyTorch-3D')
```
3. Import EfficientNet3D
```python
from efficientnet_pytorch_3d import EfficientNet3D
```
4. Define a model
```python
model = EfficientNet3D.from_name("efficientnet-b0", override_params={'num_classes': 2}, in_channels=1)
```
5. Have fun with this model :)
